<!-- END CLASS="ENLARGE_MEASURE" -->
      <div class="enlarge_html">
                  <div class="image_data">
                        <p class="caption">A salad of sunflower sprouts, grapefruit, and avocado waits to be served and eaten at a party in Washington, D.C.</p>             <span class="creditwrap"><span class="credit">Brendan Hoffman</span>/<span class="rightsnotice">Getty Images for Girl Behind The Camera</span></span>
